3. The Big 3 Protocol (Finasteride + Minoxidil + Ketoconazole)
4. Oral vs Topical Minoxidil
5. Finasteride Fears vs Facts (side effect reality check)
6. Microneedling for Hair (dermaroller protocol)
7. Hair Transplant 101 (FUE vs FUT, when to consider)
8. The Minox Beard Protocol (for facial hair)
9. Natural Supplements (Saw Palmetto, Biotin, etc.)
10. When to Just Shave It (acceptance strategy)

**Products to embed:** 8 new products (see Part 2)

**Files to create:**
- `src/data/guides/hair-loss.ts`

